<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كَشْخَنْتُه <span class="c2">(١)</span> كَشْخَنَةً: شَتَمْتَه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الخُشْكُنَانُ:</span> فارِسيٌّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الكَشْمَخَةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: بَقْلَةٌ رَخْصَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ما هذه الكَنْخَبَةُ؟: يُرِيدُ الكلامَ المُخْتَلِطَ من الخطأ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سقطت كلمة (كشخنته) من ك.<br>(٢) في ت: والكشمخة.</p> </div>